{
  "id": "adv_event_2302_01_01",
  "title": "レッツ・\nXXX・\nチャレンジ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "チョコのような甘い口づけを、あなたへ\n――ハッピーバレンタイン",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A sweet kiss like chocolate‚ to you.\n――Happy Valentine's.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.7034693718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "endTime": 8.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "い～～や～～や～～！！\nこんなん、うちは絶対認めへんからなあ～～～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ no!!\nWe absolutely won't accept this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8666666667,
      "endTime": 14.8653060595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃん落ち着いて～！\nいま本番中だってば～！　も～～～う！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan‚ calm down!\nWe're in the middle of a shooting! Nooo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0666666667,
      "endTime": 21.3153289477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "邪魔せんといて、すみれちゃん！\nトリエルの……瑠依ちゃんの純潔のためなんやー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't get in the way‚ Sumire-chan!\nIt's for TRINITYAiLE… for Rui-chan's purity!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5,
      "endTime": 27.8999999047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（う～ん……まさかこんな事態になるなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hmm… I never expected things to turn out like this…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1,
      "endTime": 32.6243762016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二週間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Two Weeks Ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6243761698,
      "endTime": 34.824376169800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "女性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今月もやってきました、マンスリー星座占い！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's time for this month's Monthly Horoscope!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7910428364,
      "endTime": 39.2243761698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "女性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あなたの気になる運勢は……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's your fortune for this month…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2243761698,
      "endTime": 41.5443761825,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2533.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　二人とも、まだいたの？\nこれから仕事の予定よね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? You two are still here?\nYou have work scheduled‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6577095031,
      "endTime": 48.333946942699995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　でも、ちょうど占い始まるところだから\nこれだけ見て行こうと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! But we thought we'd watch this before we go.\nWe just wanted to see it quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5243761698,
      "endTime": 54.495804682099994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、瑠依ちゃんも一緒に～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ Rui-chan‚ join us too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6910428364,
      "endTime": 57.3278002579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "女性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おうし座は、振り回されることが増えそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Taurus may face increased challenges…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3577105204,
      "endTime": 62.791043853699996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "女性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "踏ん張り時かも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be a time to stand firm!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7910438537,
      "endTime": 64.224377187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "女性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さそり座は、新しいことにレッツ・チャレンジ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Scorpio‚ get ready to try something new!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5910438537,
      "endTime": 68.224377187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "女性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さらなる飛躍があるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a chance for a big leap!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.224377187,
      "endTime": 70.12437718700001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "女性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うお座は、今から心構えをしっかり！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pisces‚ prepare yourself now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8910438537,
      "endTime": 74.524377187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "女性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今月は試練が訪れるかも……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There might be trials this month…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.524377187,
      "endTime": 77.5910438536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "試練の訪れ……\nなんや、先行き不安な結果やね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Trials ahead…\nIt seems like uncertain outcomes in the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.024377187,
      "endTime": 83.8465993881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんはいい感じの結果だよね\nさらなる飛躍だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have a good result‚ Rui-chan.\nAn even greater leap!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0577105204,
      "endTime": 89.3076017506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……新しいことに挑戦、か\n機会があれば、頑張ってみたいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right… trying something new‚ huh?\nIf there's an opportunity‚ I want to give it my best shot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.524377187,
      "endTime": 96.766647708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ……新たな扉を開いた瑠依ちゃんを見られるなら\n試練の一つや二つ、どんとこいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… if I get to see Rui-chan opening a new door‚\nI'm up for a challenge or two.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9577105204,
      "endTime": 104.5926698327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんは分かりやすいなぁ……あはは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan‚ you're so straightforward… Haha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.7910438537,
      "endTime": 108.6829487323,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4166.666666699995
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4166.666666699995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま……と、鈴村さんに奥山さん……\nそれに天動さんも。ちょうど良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Welcome back… to Suzumura-san‚ Okuyama-san‚ and also to Tendo-san.\nIt's perfect timing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.624377187,
      "endTime": 116.9794642209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}さん！\n……って、また名字で呼ばれた～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san!\n…Ah‚ he called us by our last names again~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1646493911,
      "endTime": 123.2392902268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロの中でうちらだけ、妙に他人行儀やから\n名字で呼ぶのはやめましょって言うたやんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Among Hoshimi Prods‚ it's just us who are oddly formal‚\nso remember how we said to stop using last names?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.5646493911,
      "endTime": 131.12246174580002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そう言えばそうだったな、ごめん\nえっと、瑠依に優、すみれ……でいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… come to think of it‚ you're right. Sorry.\nUh‚ so‚ should I call you Rui‚ Yu‚ and Sumire?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3313160578,
      "endTime": 138.980019717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふっ、なんだか新鮮ですね\nそれで、ちょうど良かった……というのは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ it feels kind of fresh.\nSo‚ what was the perfect timing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1728124935,
      "endTime": 145.8460032553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。この前少しだけ頭出しした\nバレンタインCMへの出演のことなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I met up with them about that thing.\nIt's about the Valentine's Day CM appearance…",
